name: The Greenery Cannabis Dispensary
description: A 24 hour indoor and outdoor pet friendly cannabis dispensary in Phuket that provides a variety of quality flowers and yummy but potent edibles. Our weed shop in Phuket offers delivery but also provides a safe place with free consoles, free movies, snacks and cold beverages. Our staff is ready to welcome you at any time! Consider us the 7/11 of weed shop in Thailand. A place that never sleeps. We got all the tools from disinfected bongs, papers to home made gravity bong. Our guests are from all over the world. Everybody is welcome to join The Greenery Family.

products_flowers.name: We got bud
products_flowers.description: We change our selections every few days to keep our products fresh for our valued guests. Our buds are of quality guaranteed. 24 hours open like 7/11. Prices starts at 100 Baht. Come to get the full experience. You cannot really smell the buds online.

products_prerolls.name: We roll but do not sell pre rolls - description why
products_prerolls.description: Dear guests, we do not sell prerolls as it is not allowed to do so. We will roll for you fresh on the spot. This not only gives you a better experience but also keeps its potency and freshness. Thank you for understanding.

products_edibles.name: Brownies
products_edibles.description:
Our edibles are baked by a real chef/baker who was trained by Marco Pierre White (Gordon Ramsey's teacher). These brownies have a Thai lokal landrace sativa as its base. The euphoria goes up and down with a higher intensity with every burst until you reach the peak of the journey. Best served in room temperature. DO NOT drive after.

These brownies are one of our best sellers. We keep our brownies in a temperature controlled environment to keep them fresh and potent. Enjoy!

reviews.author: Jacob
reviews.content:
Pretty neat little place to be honest.

Different range of bud as well as a range of prices.

Staff is also helpful.

The place is the only 24-hour location that I know of, which is nice.

Pretty laid back vibe. Bongs and rolling papers are available to those who want to try out their product.

Worth at least checking out in my opinion.

The customers also help make the place, it almost feels like a community.

My favorite shop, by far, in the area

reviews.content: The shop is the best cannabis dispensary in Phuket! 24 hours open and it is like the 7-11 of cannabis dispensary. Quality organic cannabis for great prices. We came in very early while other cannabis stores in Phuket are still closed. The best part of it all is that they also deliver.
